                Card elements that scale with based on width, including font
                size
              </li>
              <li>Time delayed animations</li>
              <li>Modal overlays</li>
              <li>Organised complex data</li>
              <li>No backend</li>
              <li>Keyboard shortcuts</li>
              <li>Designed for rapid browsing</li>
              <li>&gt;1million page views per year from ~80k users</li>
              <li>SEO optimised</li>
